PKG_SECTION=libs
PKG_SHORTDESC="libupnp"
PKG_LONGDESC="UPnP is an architecture that enables discovery, event notification, and control of devices on a network, independent of operating system, programming language, or physical network connection.  UPnP™ is based on common Internet standards and specifications such as TCP/IP, HTTP, and XML. For detailed information about UPnP™, including the UPnP™ Device Architecture Specification, please visit the  UPnP™ Forum web site."
